<br>
If there comes a time where I'm &quot;involved&quot; in a terrorist plot (I.E.  am on an airplane when hijackers take over) you better bet your ass they're going to have 290lbs of pissed off Canadian/American coming at them full on with intent to remove vital organs with his hands.<br>
<br>
No glory, no celebrity...I'd be doing it for me and everybody else in this country.  I'd be doing it for revenge, and for fear.  Most of all, I'd be doing it for those who have already been hurt, or potentially may be hurt by this person's actions.<br>
<br>
I'm sick of terrorism, and terrorists...I'm sick of politicians getting glory about their bills or legislations passing.  It may be my own personal misled belief...but if a persons only intent is to kill or harm or injure as many people as possible...they have NO rights.  Despite our wonderful Constitution...they do NOT deserve a fair trial if they were caught in the act.<br>
<br>
You saw what they did to the American Journalist in Pakistan.  Those people deserve NO sympathy.  They cut off his head, videotaped it, and figured it would strike fear into the hearts of Americans.  Screw them.<br>
<br>
